    <item>
      <title>在加州中央山谷，拉丁裔选民将在 2026 年选举中争夺</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/03/26/us/politics/california-latino-voters-republicans-midterms-elections.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[与该国其他拉美裔地区一样，选民将在 2024 年转向共和党。但越来越多的迹象表明，这只是昙花一现，而非持久趋势。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/03/26/us/politics/california-latino-voters-republicans-midterms-elections.html</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 26 Mar 2026 09:00:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普对欧洲的威胁使其领导人在伊朗问题上陷入双重困境</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/03/26/world/europe/iran-trump-hormuz-europe-dilemma.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[如果欧洲政客加入美国的战争，他们就有可能激怒选民。然而，如果他们不采取行动重新开放伊朗封锁的航线并缓解能源危机，他们也可能面临国内动荡。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/03/26/world/europe/iran-trump-hormuz-europe-dilemma.html</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 26 Mar 2026 04:01:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普呼吁法律打击犯罪和“流氓法官”</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/03/25/us/politics/trump-judges-rogue-law.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中期选举前，特朗普总统在一次共和党集会上表示，他希望追捕屡犯者和“流氓法官，他们是罪犯”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/03/25/us/politics/trump-judges-rogue-law.html</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 26 Mar 2026 02:49:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>国会共和党人对特朗普政府处理伊朗战争的方式感到担忧</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/03/25/world/middleeast/republicans-congress-iran-war-trump.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[共和党那些给予特朗普政府在没有国会投入的情况下发动战争的广泛自由度的议员们越来越沮丧，因为官员们几乎没有提供有关地面部队、成本或时间表的细节。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/03/25/world/middleeast/republicans-congress-iran-war-trump.html</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 26 Mar 2026 02:07:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
